    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sit the<strong> beef meatballs </strong>over the <strong>grated red onion</strong> in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 5-6 min or until the onion has started to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
